Interface SdtElement

All Known Implementing Classes:
CTSdtCell, CTSdtRow, SdtBlock, SdtRun
public interface SdtElement

This interface is implemented by the classes which represent a content control (ie SdtBlock, SdtRun, CTSdtRow, CTSdtCell).
